00:00:04.549 --> 00:00:05.549
1.

00:00:05.549 --> 00:00:10.169
Famed sex therapist Dr. Ruth Westheimer was
once a sniper of the Israeli Defense Force.

00:00:10.169 --> 00:00:14.519
She was also a survivor of the holocaust,
but unfortunately the rest of her family was

00:00:14.519 --> 00:00:15.519
killed.

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:19.410
Dr. Ruth had this to say about her sniping
days: “When I was in my routine training

00:00:19.410 --> 00:00:24.939
for the Israeli army as a teenager, they discovered
completely by chance that I was a lethal sniper.

00:00:24.939 --> 00:00:29.300
I could hit the target smack in the center
further away than anyone could believe.

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:33.300
Not just that, even though I was tiny and
not even much of an athlete, I was incredibly

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:35.649
accurate throwing hand grenades too.

00:00:35.649 --> 00:00:40.030
Even today I can load a Sten automatic rifle
in a single minute, blindfolded.”

00:00:40.030 --> 00:00:41.260
(QF 696)

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:42.260
2.

00:00:42.260 --> 00:00:45.690
While many people fear flying, nobody seems
to fear sleeping in a bed.

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:52.300
Yet in 2013, according to The Aviation Safety
Network, only 265 people around the world

00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:57.090
who traveled via a commercial airplane holding
14 or more passengers lost their lives because

00:00:57.090 --> 00:01:01.829
of a plane crash (out of about 31 million
flights), while in the United States alone,

00:01:01.829 --> 00:01:06.800
according to the Center for Disease Control,
falling out of bed accounts for about 450

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:12.660
deaths, 400,000 hospital admissions, and 1.8
million emergency room visits each year.

00:01:12.660 --> 00:01:13.660
(QF 695)

00:01:13.660 --> 00:01:14.660
3.

00:01:14.660 --> 00:01:18.440
While most people connect historical African
slave trade almost exclusively with the United

00:01:18.440 --> 00:01:23.710
States, the truth is that the U.S. was third
in this sad statistic, importing about 400,000

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:24.710
slaves.

00:01:24.710 --> 00:01:28.850
Jamaica rang in at over a million and nearly
5 million went to Brazil.

00:01:28.850 --> 00:01:29.850
(QF 690)

00:01:29.850 --> 00:01:30.850
4.

00:01:30.850 --> 00:01:33.580
