00:01:57.990 --> 00:01:58.990
6.

00:01:58.990 --> 00:02:03.321
In 1990, Chuck Norris became the first Westerner
in history to be awarded an 8th degree Black

00:02:03.321 --> 00:02:06.170
Belt (Grand Master) in Taekwondo.

00:02:06.170 --> 00:02:10.649
In his life, he’s also achieved the rankings
of 10th degree black belt in Chun Kuk Do;

00:02:10.649 --> 00:02:16.209
9th degree black belt in Tang Soo Do; and
black belts in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu and Judo.

00:02:16.209 --> 00:02:21.269
Apparently some rumors about Chuck’s supposed
superpowers might be true after all.

00:02:21.269 --> 00:02:22.269
(QF 676)

00:02:22.269 --> 00:02:23.269
